| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1566 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7e87530d-aae1-52c4-ad82-e4eb7a3853a6"
